data.description: Spectacular Country Home on 7.96 acres! Open living area w/tile flooring & wood-burning fireplace. Kitchen w/granite countertops, abundance of cabinet space, island and bkfst bar. Isolated downstairs primary suite with double sinks, soaking tub, large shower & huge walk in closet. Jack-n-Jill bedrooms down stairs plus office. Upstairs features a 2nd living area, plus 2 bedrooms and full bath.  Inviting patio, inground pool, 2 ponds, 60 x 30 shop, RV connections, solar panels & 1,500 sq ft recreational room.
